---
// v_stitch1 - Intelligence (Forge) Page (Official Brand Alignment)
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
    
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Instrument+Serif:ital,wght@0,400;1,400&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;600;700&family=Space+Mono&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

    <script is:inline src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>
    
    <script is:inline>
      tailwind.config = {
        darkMode: "class",
        theme: {
          extend: {
            colors: {
              "background": "#edece3", // Official Surface (Off White)
              "deep-authority": "#191514", // Official Base (Warm Black)
              "strategic-action": "#ff5402", // Official Action (Orange)
              "technical-sky": "#a2a1f8", // Official AI Accent (Sky)
              "muted-gray": "#a38c97", // Official Muted (Gray)
              "surface-container-high": "#e5e4d9",
            },
            fontFamily: {
              "headline": ["Instrument Serif", "serif"],
              "body": ["Instrument Sans", "sans-serif"],
              "mono": ["Space Grotesk", "monospace"],
              "label": ["Space Grotesk", "sans-serif"],
            },
            borderRadius: {"DEFAULT": "12px", "lg": "12px", "xl": "12px", "full": "9999px"},
          },
        },
      }
    </script>
    
    <style is:inline>
        body {
            background-color: #edece3 !important;
            color: #191514 !important;
            font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
        }
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
        }
        .technical-overshoot {
            position: relative;
        }
        .technical-overshoot::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: -2px;
            width: calc(100% + 4px);
            height: 1px;
            background: #191514;
            opacity: 0.2;
        }
        .dot-grid {
            background-image: radial-gradient(#191514 0.5px, transparent 0.5px);
            background-size: 24px 24px;
            opacity: 0.03;
        }
        .corner-mark::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #191514;
            border-left: 1px solid #191514;
        }
        .corner-mark::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #191514;
            border-right: 1px solid #191514;
        }
        h1, h2, h3, .font-serif { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; }
    </style>
    <title>Architecting the Future of Intelligence | The Forge</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-background text-deep-authority selection:bg-technical-sky/30">
<!-- TopNavBar -->
<header class="bg-background border-b-[0.5px] border-deep-authority/10 fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center w-full px-8 md:px-12 py-5 max-w-[1920px] mx-auto">
        <div class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tighter uppercase font-mono text-deep-authority">
            <a href="/v_stitch1">AI ADVISORY</a>
        </div>
        <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-10">
            <a class="text-deep-authority font-mono text-[12px] opacity-70 hover:text-strategic-action hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-200 uppercase tracking-wider" href="/v_stitch1/perspectives">Perspectives</a>
            <a class="text-strategic-action font-mono border-b border-strategic-action pb-0.5 text-[12px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold" href="/v_stitch1/intelligence">Intelligence</a>
            <a class="text-deep-authority font-mono text-[12px] opacity-70 hover:text-strategic-action hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-200 uppercase tracking-wider" href="#">Methodology</a>
            <a class="text-deep-authority font-mono text-[12px] opacity-70 hover:text-strategic-action hover:opacity-100 transition-all duration-200 uppercase tracking-wider" href="#">Archive</a>
        </nav>
        <button class="bg-deep-authority text-background font-mono text-[12px] px-6 py-2.5 uppercase tracking-widest active:translate-y-[-2px] active:translate-x-[-2px] active:shadow-[2px_2px_0px_#ff5402] transition-all">
            Contact Us
        </button>
    </div>
</header>

<main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-12 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="dot-grid absolute inset-0 -z-10"></div>
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="mb-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-end">
        <div class="flex-1">
            <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-muted-gray mb-8 flex items-center gap-3 font-bold">
                <span class="w-3 h-3 bg-strategic-action"></span>
                STRATEGIC PARTNERSHIP UNIT / THE FORGE
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl leading-[0.95] text-deep-authority mb-10 tracking-tight">
                Architecting the <br/>Future of <span class="italic">Intelligence.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="max-w-xl text-xl text-deep-authority/80 leading-relaxed font-serif italic">
                The Forge is our high-conviction partnership program designed for industrial leaders ready to integrate sovereign AI architectures. We don't just advise; we engineer.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 aspect-square relative corner-mark p-6">
            <div class="w-full h-full overflow-hidden border border-deep-authority/10">
                <img alt="Modern architectural detail" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale opacity-80 mix-blend-multiply" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC50m0nS_slztsm0mK8rGsUe0kaoiihKxhWclC2pmX-_vxaBP5nrBHKSJzG3AMvId3_ww_zePBqC_sxNMWQNx9fEQaOUnklE3FON_5J13JodTAXKEG-qpTw_O83N8X90ltBNFQCqNMbWoWwDRLvK-VqrOSN6k0jD1PjEeLgjveFa3j55SFPwWbUfV8bBn8fRhM0pYYusPhPUzIR8ta5XAyzErS3hNo3akI1Vtp8G8iFRhuoApHIhQQVc1TVuIRv7ZqTdINmndEFC751"/>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-background p-5 border-l border-b border-deep-authority/10">
                <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-gray font-bold">
                    REF: DS_LOG_FORGE_01
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Onboarding Form Section -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-20 items-start">
        <!-- Context Side (Left) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-16">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="font-mono text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-strategic-action">Technical Audit</h3>
                <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-gray italic font-serif font-bold">Every partnership begins with a rigorous baseline audit of your existing data infrastructure and operational readiness.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="font-mono text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-technical-sky">Sovereign Deployment</h3>
                <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-muted-gray italic font-serif font-bold">Customized LLM frameworks hosted within your private perimeter, ensuring zero-leakage of proprietary strategic logic.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-surface-container-high/30 p-10 border-l-4 border-deep-authority relative">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute top-6 right-6 opacity-20 text-2xl text-deep-authority">contract</span>
                <p class="text-3xl italic mb-6 font-serif leading-snug text-deep-authority">"The Forge is where theoretical potential meets structural reality."</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-gray opacity-60 font-bold">— Dr. Alistair Thorne, Chief Architect</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Form Side (Right) -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 bg-surface-container-high/30 border border-deep-authority/5 p-10 md:p-20 relative">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-6 border-l border-b border-deep-authority/10 font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-gray tracking-widest font-bold">
                PARTNER_ONBOARDING_V1.0.2
            </div>
            <form class="space-y-16">
                <!-- Section 01: Entity Details -->
                <div class="space-y-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-background bg-deep-authority px-3 py-1 font-bold">01</span>
                        <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-deep-authority">Entity Identification</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-10">
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <label class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray block font-bold">Legal Entity Name</label>
                            <input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-deep-authority/10 focus:border-strategic-action focus:ring-0 p-0 py-3 text-base placeholder:text-deep-authority/20 font-sans tracking-tight text-deep-authority" placeholder="e.g. STRATOS GLOBAL HOLDINGS" type="text"/>
                        </div>
                        <div class="space-y-2">
                            <label class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray block font-bold">Primary Sector</label>
                            <select class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-deep-authority/10 focus:border-strategic-action focus:ring-0 p-0 py-3 text-base font-sans cursor-pointer text-deep-authority">
                                <option>Industrial Manufacturing</option>
                                <option>Financial Infrastructure</option>
                                <option>Logistics &amp; Supply Chain</option>
                                <option>Sovereign Technology</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Section 02: Scale & Intent -->
                <div class="space-y-10">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                        <span class="font-mono text-[11px] text-background bg-deep-authority px-3 py-1 font-bold">02</span>
                        <h2 class="font-mono text-[12px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-deep-authority">Structural Intent</h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <label class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray block font-bold">Strategic Objective (Abstract)</label>
                        <textarea class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b-2 border-deep-authority/10 focus:border-strategic-action focus:ring-0 p-0 py-3 text-base placeholder:text-deep-authority/20 font-sans resize-none leading-relaxed tracking-tight text-deep-authority" placeholder="Briefly describe the operational bottleneck your organization intends to resolve via AI architectural intervention..." rows="3"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                        <label class="group cursor-pointer">
                            <input class="hidden peer" type="checkbox"/>
                            <div class="border-2 border-deep-authority/10 p-5 text-center peer-checked:bg-deep-authority peer-checked:text-background transition-all hover:border-strategic-action">
                                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Data Audit</span>
                            </div>
                        </label>
                        <label class="group cursor-pointer">
                            <input class="hidden peer" type="checkbox"/>
                            <div class="border-2 border-deep-authority/10 p-5 text-center peer-checked:bg-deep-authority peer-checked:text-background transition-all hover:border-strategic-action">
                                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Custom LLM</span>
                            </div>
                        </label>
                        <label class="group cursor-pointer">
                            <input class="hidden peer" type="checkbox"/>
                            <div class="border-2 border-deep-authority/10 p-5 text-center peer-checked:bg-deep-authority peer-checked:text-background transition-all hover:border-strategic-action">
                                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Edge Compute</span>
                            </div>
                        </label>
                        <label class="group cursor-pointer">
                            <input class="hidden peer" type="checkbox"/>
                            <div class="border-2 border-deep-authority/10 p-5 text-center peer-checked:bg-deep-authority peer-checked:text-background transition-all hover:border-strategic-action">
                                <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-widest font-bold">Governance</span>
                            </div>
                        </label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- CTA Section -->
                <div class="pt-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center justify-between gap-10 border-t-2 border-deep-authority/10">
                    <p class="font-mono text-[11px] text-muted-gray max-w-xs leading-relaxed tracking-widest font-bold">
                        BY SUBMITTING THIS MANIFESTO, YOU ACKNOWLEDGE THE REQUIREMENT FOR TECHNICAL DISCLOSURE UPON ACCEPTANCE.
                    </p>
                    <button class="bg-strategic-action text-background font-mono text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] px-12 py-6 transition-all hover:-translate-y-1 hover:-translate-x-1 hover:shadow-[6px_6px_0px_#191514] active:translate-y-0 active:translate-x-0 active:shadow-none" type="submit">
                        Partner with Us
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="bg-background border-t-4 border-deep-authority pt-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-16 px-8 md:px-12 py-20 w-full max-w-[1920px] mx-auto border-x border-deep-authority/5">
        <div class="col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
            <div class="text-sm font-black tracking-[0.3em] text-deep-authority mb-10 uppercase font-mono">
                AI ADVISORY
            </div>
            <p class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray leading-relaxed max-w-[220px] font-bold">
                © 2024 AI ADVISORY. ARCHITECTURAL MASTER PLAN v1.0.2 / ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-5">
            <span class="font-mono text-[12px] font-bold mb-6 opacity-40 uppercase tracking-widest">SERVICES</span>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Strategic Services</a>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Technical Audits</a>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Operational AI</a>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Governance</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col space-y-5">
            <span class="font-mono text-[12px] font-bold mb-6 opacity-40 uppercase tracking-widest">RESOURCES</span>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Whitepapers</a>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Case Studies</a>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">System Status</a>
            <a class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-muted-gray hover:text-technical-sky transition-colors font-bold" href="#">Privacy Index</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between items-end h-full">
            <div class="flex gap-6">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 border-2 border-deep-authority/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-technical-sky transition-colors cursor-pointer text-deep-authority">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">terminal</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-10 h-10 border-2 border-deep-authority/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-technical-sky transition-colors cursor-pointer text-deep-authority">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">grid_view</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-deep-authority text-background p-5 font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] text-right leading-loose">
                LAT: 51.5074° N<br/>LNG: 0.1278° W
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
